#[navbar]

#[section, $md:
    @../ (Documentation) / Values and bindings

    # Values and bindings

    Names are cheap. Copies aren't automatic. Existing values are shared by default, mutability is explicit and `copy` is the line between another view and an independent value.

    These rules apply to every type. The memory-management pages explain how the compiler validates and lowers them.
]

